B. The Relevant Policy Terms
A. The Policy's Exclusion J Precludes Coverage Because Hemmendinger, In His Role as Receiver, Acts on Behalf of "the Organization"

2. A Suit by Hemmendinger in His Role As Receiver Is, In Legal Effect, a Suit By ProCAP
